4
00:00:06,284 --> 00:00:07,962
is MSP.

5
00:00:07,962 --> 00:00:10,973
The legalisation of Minimum Support Price.

6
00:00:10,973 --> 00:00:11,663
"MSP"

7
00:00:11,663 --> 00:00:13,099
"Minimum Support Price"

8
00:00:13,099 --> 00:00:14,636
"MSP for all crops."

9
00:00:14,636 --> 00:00:16,872
Many news anchors and YouTubers claim that

10
00:00:16,872 --> 00:00:19,230
if the government fulfils this demand

11
00:00:19,230 --> 00:00:21,054
then it will completely destroy the country's economy.

12
00:00:21,054 --> 00:00:24,847
