onions for ₹2 and garlic for ₹0.50.

34
00:01:28,911 --> 00:01:31,719
They should have a guarantee of a minimum price.

35
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:34,304
Like MRP, MSP is also very logical,

36
00:01:34,304 --> 00:01:38,416
that's why most politicians have always favoured it.

37
00:01:38,416 --> 00:01:42,021
Like BJP leader Narendra Modi before 2014.

38
00:01:42,021 --> 00:01:43,288
