53
00:02:13,551 --> 00:02:14,834
A big round of applause for him.

54
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,418
And not only the problem,

55
00:02:16,418 --> 00:02:17,713
he gives us the solution too.

56
00:02:17,713 --> 00:02:18,565
Listen further.

57
00:02:18,565 --> 00:02:20,175
"Brothers and sisters,

58
00:02:20,175 --> 00:02:22,671
we have stated in our manifesto,

59
00:02:22,671 --> 00:02:31,404
that we will decide the MSP 
