60
00:02:31,404 --> 00:02:34,888
"That is why we have said that 
the cost of input for the farmer,

61
00:02:34,888 --> 00:02:40,964
water, labour, electricity, 
seeds, fertilisers, medicines,

62
00:02:40,964 --> 00:02:43,651
whatever the cost is,

63
